OL,5, The cap on bankers' bonuses is being   
OL,6, removed as part of a post-Brexit       
OL,7, shake-up of UK financial rules, it has 
OL,8, been confirmed.                        
OL,10,FThe decision was first announced by    
OL,11,Fformer chancellor Kwasi Kwarteng last  
OL,12,Fyear, who said it would make London a  
OL,13,Fmore attractive place to do business.  
OL,15,FIt was one of the few policies from Mr 
OL,16,FKwarteng's mini-budget to remain after 
OL,17,Fmost were unwound by his successor.    
OL,19,FThe cap on bonuses will be lifted from 
OL,20,F31 October, the regulator said.        
